    // a. The report should include the following
    // b. Each section should have an underlined heading.
    // c. The introduction, the middle sections and the closing section(s)
    // d. A report is organized in sections.
    // e. (Not listed in Q1 text but present in options 'e'). 
    // Wait, Q2 starts with "a. It is about cultivating...".
    // Options for Q1: A. d e b a c.
    // Let's assume 'e' is missing from text or it's a typo in my reading.
