    options: [".d e c a b", "b a e d c", "b d e c a", "d a e c a"],
    // b. I believe in power of education (Topic).
    // a. It is about cultivating mind (Definition).
    // d. Learning can be same for anyone... (Equality).
    // e. So money doesn't matter... (Example 1).
    // c. Also color doesn't matter (Example 2).
    // Order: b a d e c. Or b a e d c?
